{"tid":1837613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】食衛局與口罩供應商溝通 張建宗：下星期有幾批抵港","createTime":"2020-01-23T16:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:28:35.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eb41ec9aacd64e07c2c0a0ec428d1398b9e7ee69","tid":1837613,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】食衛局與口罩供應商溝通 張建宗：下星期有幾批抵港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200123/_2020012319493324975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200123%2F_2020012319493324975.jpg&h=d5d7524d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民搶購口罩。<br />\n武漢肺炎爆發，本港市民搶購口罩，有藥房更坐地起價。署理行政長官張建宗晚上舉行記者會，張建宗指，衛生署會加強對懷疑新型肺炎個案監測及更新對呈報準則，就懷疑及確診個案設立朝8晚9熱線（2125 1122），讓與懷疑病患接觸者致電。政府會每日開記者會，增加透明度。而食物及衞生局正密切與口罩供應商溝通，而下星期會有好幾批口罩抵港。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，麥理浩夫人度假村已經投入應用作隔離營，鯉魚門度假村都會改成檢疫營。張建宗又指，教育局呼籲學校與內地交流團延遲出發。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗續指，衛生署及醫管局已經有3個月口罩、保護醫物儲備，食物及衞生局與零售商、供應商溝通，明天會開緊急會議，下星期會有好幾批口罩抵達。而政府正積極向供應商爭取儘快將口罩送到本港。他又呼籲，市民如無必要不要到武漢，如果一定要去應該回港後佩戴口罩14天，市民到人多的地方亦應戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n陳漢儀指，衞生署電話熱線截至下午4時接收到71個查詢。<br />\n<br />\n更新時間：2038<br />\n建立時間：1945<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200123/_2020012319493439417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200123%2F_2020012319493439417.jpg&h=3c54a03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200123/_2020012319493618346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200123%2F_2020012319493618346.jpg&h=155c0a86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba5d74df03dd7580081dac11bed4fedf672be518","tid":1837613,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"幾批=?"},{"pid":"cfac5af70f957d0dcad6d14560d4bbcaa4bec099","tid":1837613,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"下星期死撚左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9f79b4a031e632a16c52400a6c18e21031f4c","tid":1837613,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"推上去重要野！<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d1275552f794fb603e2f26b5ca58935c2600870","tid":1837613,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"幾批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed08c5300a01acfd5629d8d9e9860f9839253d7","tid":1837613,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"具體D 好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d218f2e7117fcfd38457ab5d45711bc74cb02e","tid":1837613,"uid":70923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"幾批到香港然後藥房賣$1000一盒？屌你老母張建宗人哋澳門政府自己買成本價賣俾市民，你幾十萬一個月做緊啲乜嘢？食屎啦張建宗"},{"pid":"b0851856b0baeb1b56e85f048b447c57c0862c51","tid":1837613,"uid":4964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"下星期都有幾批中國人嚟幫你掃晒佢"},{"pid":"829419cce81d09df6d38d28d4a8c83447f4da112","tid":1837613,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"我真心想知來源係邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3cc0f062de6c974269e6a354bc00b7e9747323","tid":1837613,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"下星期 你唔撚好等到死哂先黎?"},{"pid":"88febd713683fefa1cdec9bc71c68ca610930bc1","tid":1837613,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:08:05.000Z","msg"